      "en": "Under the hood, many practical implementations of cloud services are still built on a central pattern: a third party’s data center delivers compute and services to many customers. That centralization has consequences.",
      "it": "",
      "source": "blog-posts/2026-04-23-the-future-of-cloud-what-cloud-really-means-why-its-centralized-and-what-comes-next.html",
